[preface]
== Introduction

New Democracy is different from current Democracy in that you personally can change it. What you read here is not set in stone. It is not a constitution, nor is it the premise to one.

New Democracy is a call to action. If you want to take action to improve our current Democracy then you are encouraged to join New Democracy. New Democray is like an ocean. Things are constantly moving around within it and its shape conforms the the landscape of life's cirucomstances that are constantly changing. 

New Democracy, noun: 1. Society of the people, by the people, and for the people. Otherwise, everything else is new. Well new  relative to New Democracy. :)

New Democracy dispenses with government all together. It is not anarchy. In fact, New Democracy will require of everyone far more social responsibility than Old Democracy.

New Democracy replaces government with society. New Democracy manages society as society and not as government. That is why the definition starts with the word society. New Democracy is not a government.

=Society and Happy People

New Democracy has no distinction between what we call government today and the rest of society. It is just society.

How do you like your eggs? My current go to is as follows:

1. 2 eggs broken into a mixing bowl
2. 1 tablespoon of milk, usually coconut milk
3. 1/2 tablespoon of Worcestershire sauce
4. A dash of turmeric and paprika
5. A tablespoon of blue cheese crumbles

New Democracy includes food recipes. New Democracy encapsulates all of life.

Happy people can create happy life. Miserable cannot. There has never been a more miserable lot than those who run the US government today. Misery is can be our only expectation then.

Requiring leaders to be happy people is a society mandate, not a governing mandate. No government in existence can require leaders to be happy. New Democracy demands it. Show us your happiness!

This doesn't mean everyone's perception of happiness it the same or that happy people will produce happy results. Bill Clinton genuinely appeared to be a happy person on the surface. When it came to women though he was an abuser. New Democracy would not allow Bill Clinton to lead anywhere near women. Which is fine.

New Democracy plays to everyone's strengths and downplays weaknesses. Old Democracy doesn't take social well being of leaders into account.

As you read through this document you will find the happy. Stories and recipes. :)

If you follow me on social media then you know I decorate my feed. All my posts have an art image attached. This is because I'm happy even as I champion social change by expanding on our current social problems.

Be happy and happy results may follow. If you are not happy then you are very much needed and welcome, but best not to lead.


